metadata.name: St. Patrick's Day- by SAWA #1/50
metadata.description:
Brief story: Sienna lived in a small town on Bae island. Sienna loved the month of March because it meant that St. Patrick's Day was just around the corner. She would spend weeks preparing for the holiday, getting her green outfit and shamrock accessories ready.  
On the morning of St. Patrick's Day, She watched the parade go by, cheering and clapping along with everyone else.
